name: Dont Call Me a Devil
author: UpdatingStatusOnGoingTypeManhua
content: The sacred heavenly gate looms high in the boundless sky, while the abyss of time and space wreaks havoc upon the world. As twelve spiritual springs rise from the earth and the moon slips beyond humanity’s grasp… where will our destiny lead? The realm of gods? The domain of demons? No, this is a world that belongs to humanity!I will claim the crown that no one else dares to bear and rise as the king of a new era.My name is Ren Jie, and to live is to be extraordinary! Original Webtoon
